# Approach
We are aldready having row vectors in grid, so take column vectors in another 2D array type, and compare both of them. If found similar, increase the answer by 1.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(n^2). As this is Beginner friendly, it takes O(n^2) time to solve the problem 

- Space complexity:
O(n^2). It takes one 2D vector, to store. So O(n^2) space complexity.
