We pre calculated the bit count and saved it in an array.
Now we will do the number of pairs greater than k to find the ans in nlog (n) time .
For that we will first sort the array and the find the array greater than or equal to k-arr[i] using lower_bound function. all the elements after that element will also be in our answer so we will add arr.size()-j to our answer.
