# Approach
First, we defined a set for removing the duplicate element from array.
Then we create a vector for storing the set bits of every elemnt of the array.Then we sort the array and use simple two pointer approch to count the pairs whose sum greater than or equal to k. We can also use binary search in place of two pointer.

